{# 
    Bidirectional Text Override (<bdo>)
    ===========================================================================
    Overrides the current text direction.

    Variables:
    - `bdo_dir`: The text direction. Can be "ltr" (left-to-right) or "rtl" (right-to-left). Defaults to "ltr".
    - `bdo_text`: The text to be displayed with the specified direction. Defaults to "Sample text".

    Notes:
    - The `| e` filter is used to escape any special characters in the variables to prevent XSS attacks.

    Links:
    - https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdo
    - https://www.w3schools.com/tags/tag_bdo.asp

#}

<bdo dir="{{ bdo_dir | default('ltr') | e }}">
    {{ bdo_text | default('Sample text') | e }}
</bdo>
